    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - May 1, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-05-01/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 May 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-05-01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Indian CIOs and CISOs need to adopt certain crucial practices: Dell EMC&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of the recent reports revealed, 33 reported data breaches leading to almost 36.6 million data records being compromised in India during 2016, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dqindia.com/indian-cios-and-cisos-need-to-adopt-certain-crucial-practices-dell-emc/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.dqindia.com/indian-cios-and-cisos-need-to-adopt-certain-crucial-practices-dell-emc/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Study the landscape to find, face common business challenges&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Businesses are becoming more proactive as they attempt to protect themselves against data breaches, but often aren&amp;rsquo;t mobilizing until there&amp;rsquo;s a &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.sbnonline.com/article/study-landscape-face-common-business-challenges/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.sbnonline.com/article/study-landscape-face-common-business-challenges/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Who&amp;rsquo;s behind data breaches globally &amp;amp; what tactics do they use&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ETtech.com Cyberespionage is now the most common type of attack seen in manufacturing, the public sector and now education, according to the Verizon 2017 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://tech.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/corporate/whos-behind-data-breaches-globally-what-tactics-do-they-use-infographic/58453430&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://tech.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/corporate/whos-behind-data-breaches-globally-what-tactics-do-they-use-infographic/58453430&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Carbon Black: How to set up a threat hunting program&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It might be necessary to carve out time from the work schedules of existing staff for threat hunting. Depending on an organisation&amp;rsquo;s size, the time spent &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://securitybrief.co.nz/story/carbon-black-how-set-threat-hunting-program/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://securitybrief.co.nz/story/carbon-black-how-set-threat-hunting-program/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon Finds Phishing Attacks, Malware Top Data Breach Causes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The latest Verizon data breach report showed that phishing attacks are on the rise, with 43 percent of data breaches stemming from such incidents.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/verizon-finds-phishing-attacks-malware-top-data-breach-causes&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/verizon-finds-phishing-attacks-malware-top-data-breach-causes&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cyberespionage and ransomware on the rise&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;51% of data breaches analyzed involved malware. 66% of malware was installed via malicious email attachments. Ransomware rose to the fifth most &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.enterpriseinnovation.net/article/cyberespionage-and-ransomware-rise-1560284726&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.enterpriseinnovation.net/article/cyberespionage-and-ransomware-rise-1560284726&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Nyansa premieres new Voyance network analytics tools&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Phishing is fundamental. More than 40% of data breaches used phishing, with the technique popular in both cyberespionage and financially driven &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/news/450417793/Nyansa-premieres-new-Voyance-network-analytics-tools&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/news/450417793/Nyansa-premieres-new-Voyance-network-analytics-tools&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;One-Third of Federal Agencies Reported Data Breaches in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nearly all (96%) respondents consider themselves &amp;ldquo;vulnerable&amp;rdquo; to data breaches; about half (48%) state they are &amp;ldquo;very&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;extremely&amp;rdquo; vulnerable.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/one-third-of-federal-agencies-reported-data-breaches-in-2016/d/d-id/1328772&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/one-third-of-federal-agencies-reported-data-breaches-in-2016/d/d-id/1328772&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Physical Security Information Management (PSIM) Market is expected to grow&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trade Calls (press release) Global Physical Security Information Management (PSIM) Market Research Report 2017 provides a unique tool for evaluating the market, highlighting &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.tradecalls.org/2017-05-01-physical-security-information-management-psim-market&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.tradecalls.org/2017-05-01-physical-security-information-management-psim-market&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Informational: Symantec Endpoint Protection Computer List Changed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informational: Symantec Endpoint Protection Computer List Changed&amp;rdquo;.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.symantec.com/connect/forums/informational-symantec-endpoint-protection-computer-list-changed-1&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.symantec.com/connect/forums/informational-symantec-endpoint-protection-computer-list-changed-1&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches: It&amp;rsquo;s still personal&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a blog post last September, I highlighted how data breaches for the first half of 2016 shifted from stolen credit card data and financial information to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3193155/security/data-breaches-its-still-personal.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3193155/security/data-breaches-its-still-personal.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;IBM X-Force Finds +937% More Fin Svc Records Breached, +29% Attacks In 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The new IBM X Force report once again demonstrates the escalating threat of data breaches that every organization is now facing, and underscores &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.informationsecuritybuzz.com/expert-comments/ibm-x-force-finds-937-fin-svc-records-breached-29-attacks-2016/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.informationsecuritybuzz.com/expert-comments/ibm-x-force-finds-937-fin-svc-records-breached-29-attacks-2016/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
